  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div role=\"note\" class=\"hatnote navigation-not-searchable\" style=\"font-style: italic;padding-left: 1.6em;margin-bottom: 0.5em;\">For the TV episode, see <a href=\"/index.php/The_Burning_Mill\" title=\"The Burning Mill\">The Burning Mill</a>.</div>\n<table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;background: #B0C4DE; text-align:center;\">Battle of the Burning Mill</th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Burning_Mill_and_Stone_Hedge_map.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Burning Mill and Stone Hedge map.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/Burning_Mill_and_Stone_Hedge_map.png/400px-Burning_Mill_and_Stone_Hedge_map.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"255\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/2/2b/Burning_Mill_and_Stone_Hedge_map.png/600px-Burning_Mill_and_Stone_Hedge_map.png 1.5x, /images/2/2b/Burning_Mill_and_Stone_Hedge_map.png 2x\" /></a><div><div style=\"width:100%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa;\">Map of the Battle of the Burning Mill and the <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_Stone_Hedge\" title=\"Taking of Stone Hedge\">Taking of Stone Hedge</a></div></div></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Conflict</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Date</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/129_AC\" title=\"129 AC\">129&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Place</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Burning_Mill\" title=\"Burning Mill\">Burning Mill</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Result</th><td>\nVictory for the <a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">blacks</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<table style=\"width:100%; text-align:left;\">\n<tbody><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Combatants</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\"><img alt=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/32px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/48px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/5/5f/Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg/64px-Rhaenyra_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></b>/<b><a href=\"/index.php/Blacks\" title=\"Blacks\">Blacks</a></b>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\"><img alt=\"House Blackwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/20px-House_Blackwood.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/30px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/40px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\">House Blackwood</a></li></ul></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\"><a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\"><img alt=\"Aegon II Targaryen.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/32px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/48px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg/64px-Aegon_II_Targaryen.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <b><a href=\"/index.php/House_Targaryen\" title=\"House Targaryen\">House Targaryen</a></b>/<b><a href=\"/index.php/Greens\" title=\"Greens\">Greens</a></b>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\"><img alt=\"House Bracken.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/20px-House_Bracken.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/30px-House_Bracken.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/40px-House_Bracken.svg.png 2x\" /></a>&#160;<a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\">House Bracken</a></li></ul></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Commanders</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\"><img alt=\"House Blackwood.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/20px-House_Blackwood.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/30px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e1/House_Blackwood.svg/40px-House_Blackwood.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Blackwood\" title=\"Samwell Blackwood\">Samwell Blackwood</a></td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\"><img alt=\"House Bracken.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/20px-House_Bracken.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/30px-House_Bracken.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/e5/House_Bracken.svg/40px-House_Bracken.svg.png 2x\" /></a> Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Amos_Bracken\" title=\"Amos Bracken\">Amos Bracken</a><br />Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Raylon_Rivers\" title=\"Raylon Rivers\">Raylon Rivers</a></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center;\"><b>Casualties</b></td></tr><tr><td width=\"50%\" style=\"border-right:1px dotted #aaa;\">Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Blackwood\" title=\"Samwell Blackwood\">Samwell Blackwood</a>†</td>\n    <td width=\"50%\">                                      Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Amos_Bracken\" title=\"Amos Bracken\">Amos Bracken</a>†</td></tr>\n</tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p>The <b>Battle of the Burning Mill</b> took place near the start of <a href=\"/index.php/Dance_of_the_Dragons\" title=\"Dance of the Dragons\">Dance of the Dragons</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> As the preceding <a href=\"/index.php/Assault_on_Harrenhal\" title=\"Assault on Harrenhal\">fall of Harrenhal</a> had been bloodless, it was the first true battle in the civil war between opposing armies in the field.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_of_the_Burning_Mill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php/House_Blackwood\" title=\"House Blackwood\">House Blackwood</a> declared for Queen <a href=\"/index.php/Rhaenyra_Targaryen\" title=\"Rhaenyra Targaryen\">Rhaenyra Targaryen</a> when war broke out, while <a href=\"/index.php/House_Bracken\" title=\"House Bracken\">House Bracken</a> supported her half-brother, King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon II Targaryen\">Aegon II Targaryen</a>. Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Samwell_Blackwood\" title=\"Samwell Blackwood\">Samwell Blackwood</a> sent raiders into Bracken lands, causing Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Amos_Bracken\" title=\"Amos Bracken\">Amos Bracken</a> to march on Blackwood territory in response. The Blackwoods surprised the Brackens while they were camped by <a href=\"/index.php/Burning_Mill\" title=\"Burning Mill\">a mill</a> near a river, possibly the <a href=\"/index.php/Red_Fork\" title=\"Red Fork\">Red Fork</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>Amos slew Lord Blackwood in single combat during the ensuing battle. The Bracken <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knight</a> was himself slain by a <a href=\"/index.php/Weirwood\" title=\"Weirwood\">weirwood</a> arrow said to have been fired by Samwell's sister, <a href=\"/index.php/Alysanne_Blackwood\" title=\"Alysanne Blackwood\">Alysanne</a>. The mill was put to the torch during the hours of fighting. Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Raylon_Rivers\" title=\"Raylon Rivers\">Raylon Rivers</a> eventually led the Bracken survivors in retreat to <a href=\"/index.php/Stone_Hedge\" title=\"Stone Hedge\">Stone Hedge</a>, but the Bracken castle had been <a href=\"/index.php/Taking_of_Stone_Hedge\" title=\"Taking of Stone Hedge\">taken</a> in the meantime by Prince <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_Targaryen\" title=\"Daemon Targaryen\">Daemon Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtpatq.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Battle_of_the_Burning_Mill&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.2</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtwoiaf_the_targaryen_kings:_aegon_ii.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.3</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/The_World_of_Ice_%26_Fire\" title=\"The World of Ice &amp; Fire\">The World of Ice &amp; Fire</a></i>, The Targaryen Kings: Aegon II.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rfabthe_dying_of_the_dragons_-_the_red_dragon_and_the_gold.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#c